This audience is willing to listen to and judge Bar, but based on civilized changes of arguments, and not within the framework of what many people perceive as a chase-gatherer (seeking "public debate," Barrick Gold has just placed a request regarding the authors of Noir Canada urging them not to use this word anymore).
