The limitation means that if the ministry buys in the framework of an auction, an extra tax will be imposed on the golden parachutes unless the bank's failed boss retires.
By buying the bad loans directly, the government will intervene aggressively to ensure that bosses' compensation is not exaggerated.
In addition to the above, existing golden parachute contracts will not be changed, the limitations relate only to new contracts to stimulate participation in the programme as well.
